; Positive comments are those with a polarity score greater than 0; 
; Clean comments refer to those with minimal or no profanity, i.e., a profanity score less than 0.1; 
; Recent comments are those with the most recent creation times.

- High Confidence: Aspect sentiment analysis confidence greater than 0.8; 
- Medium Confidence: Aspect sentiment analysis confidence between 0.5 and 0.8; 
- Low Confidence: Aspect sentiment analysis confidence less than 0.5.
